<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n42068d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42068d">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42068d"> 68(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> let it alone</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[some of souls of Faithful, on encountering new soul]</font> ask it, &ldquo;What hath such an one done, and such an one? how are they? &hellip; And some of them say, &ldquo;<mark>Let it alone</mark> &hellip; ask it when it is at rest.&rdquo; <small> Stanley Lane-Poole, <a name="SLPS" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#SLPS"><cite title="source">The Speeches and Table-Talk of the Prophet Mohammad</cite></a> (1882) 173</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
